WEBVTT

00:07.040 --> 00:09.668
What dog did he steal that sweater from?

00:10.710 --> 00:12.200
Probably his wife.

00:15.982 --> 00:18.041
Good God, who shot the couch?

00:21.154 --> 00:25.147
Give her a break, Hilary.
She just won the Kentucky Derby.

00:27.827 --> 00:30.625
Who's that lady with Nell Carter?

00:30.730 --> 00:33.528
That's not Nell Carter. That's my father!

00:36.302 --> 00:38.327
God, you're so shallow. I hate you.

00:38.405 --> 00:40.498
You're stupid and ugly
and I wish you would die.

00:40.573 --> 00:42.097
- Sorry.
- Okay.

00:43.309 --> 00:45.607
Look at her!

00:46.646 --> 00:50.082
Brake! Hit the brake, Will!

00:50.950 --> 00:54.181
- What in the hell are you doing?
- I'm sorry. It ain't my fault.

00:54.254 --> 00:57.189
I panicked.
That squirrel came out of nowhere.

00:57.290 --> 01:00.054
Philip, I'll call the manager
and have him remove the cart.

01:00.126 --> 01:02.686
Oh, let's just draw more attention
to ourselves.

01:02.762 --> 01:05.697
- Get in the cart, Vivian.
- No.

01:07.934 --> 01:12.894
I'm sorry, Mr. Banks,
but no golf carts in the dining room.

01:14.841 --> 01:17.708
You've certainly made a name
at this country club.

01:17.777 --> 01:21.213
I wouldn't be surprised if they revoked
our shuffleboard privileges.

01:21.881 --> 01:25.408
That's fine with me.
This place is wack. I'm out of here.

01:25.652 --> 01:27.244
Hold up.

01:27.754 --> 01:31.690
Special bulletin. Hormones to Will.

01:33.193 --> 01:35.718
Hold up yourself, Will.
That's Mimi Mumford.

01:36.563 --> 01:40.397
You can't get to first base with her
unless you impress her father.

01:40.700 --> 01:43.533
He's an eminent surgeon,
a championship polo player...

01:43.603 --> 01:46.595
and around these parts,
he's known as Dr. No.

01:46.673 --> 01:49.836
- Why do they call him that?
- Because he never says "yes."

01:50.276 --> 01:52.836
No young man is good enough
for his daughter.

01:53.046 --> 01:56.743
He ain't gonna have a chance to tell me no
'cause I ain't gonna ask.

01:57.083 --> 02:00.177
Mimi, if you're not busy on Friday night...

02:00.253 --> 02:02.847
would you like to accompany me
to the Apple Blossom ball?

02:02.922 --> 02:03.911
No.

02:05.825 --> 02:07.452
What's your name, boy?

02:09.062 --> 02:11.792
What school do you go to?
What college are you applying to?

02:11.865 --> 02:13.628
What's your career plans?

02:13.700 --> 02:16.863
I'm just a sophomore, sir.
I don't really know yet.

02:16.936 --> 02:19.029
Out of here, son. You disgust me.

